    "long_instructions": "Organize this song into `intro`, `chorus`, and `verse` functions. The song itself should not change; only how it is organized. You can accomplish this by dragging-and-dropping the existing code into the [functions that are already provided](#clickable=id-down:intro_function---verse_function), then dragging the function calls underneath When Run. When you are finished, you should have 3 functions being called in your program:\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/8569ef83b4f04d7f087838d319aadb43-image-1740586923318.png)",
